   <body>
      <p>With the <i>Customer Incentive Manager User Guide</i>, you can find out how Apttus Customer Incentive Manager works and how to set-up the Customer Incentive Manager.</p>
      <p>
         <table>
            <tgroup cols="2">
               <colspec colname="col1"/>
               <colspec colname="col2"/>
               <thead>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Topic</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Description</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>What's Covered</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Customer Incentive Manager User Guide is designed to provide users with information on setting up billing program using Customer Incentive Manager. It covers information, step-by-step instructions, and use cases for the features provided by Apttus Customer Incentive Manager.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Primary Audience</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>
                           <ul>
                              <li>Contract Analysts</li>
                              <li>Contract Manager</li>
                              <li>Program Manager</li>
                           </ul>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>IT Environment</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Refer to the latest <i>Customer Incentive Manager on Azure Release Notes</i> for information on System Requirements and Supported Platforms.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Updates</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>For a comprehensive list of updates to this guide for each release, refer to <xref href="../what_s_new_102432686/102432686.xml" format="dita">What's New</xref> topic.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Other Resources</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>
                           <ul>
                              <li>Contract Management User Guide: Refer to this guide for information about agreements.</li>
                              <li>CPQ Administrator Guide: Refer this guide for setting up products, price lists, and constraint rules.</li>
                           </ul>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
      </p>
      <p>This guide describes the following tasks: </p>
      <ul>
         <li>Configuring the application according to your organizational needs.</li>
         <li>Creating month-end billing program, reward savings program, bundle savings program, package saving program, and partnership savings program.</li>
         <li>Performing on-demand validations on agreements</li>
         <li>Duplicating sections</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Before using Customer Incentive Manager, you must be familiar with the following:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>Basic Apttus Omni administration</li>
         <li>Apttus CPQ and Contract Management administration</li>
         <li>Azure Platform and Apttus terms and definitions</li>
      </ul>
      <p>If you are new to Apttus Customer Incentive Manager, begin here: <xref href="../getting-started_102432688_102432688/102432688.xml"
               format="dita">Getting Started</xref> and <xref href="../about_customer_incentive__102432687/102432687.xml"
               format="dita">About Customer Incentive Manager</xref>.</p>
